title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Isuzu D-MAX 2013-17 3.0L 4JJ1-TDX Dual / Single Battery Diesel – Pre Filter Separator Kit Fuel Manager FM631DPK

content.rendered:
Fuel Manager FM631DPK Pre Filter Kit for:
Fuel Filter Water Separator

Isuzu D-MAX 4JJ1-TDX 3.0L 2013-17
CRD Diesel Dual / Single Battery
Isuzu D-MAX MU-X 4JJ1-TDX 3.0L 2013-17
CRD Diesel Dual / Single Battery

This filter unit is to be used as a Pre-Filter to separate water and contaminates thus avoiding costly repairs due to poor fuel quality. Comes complete with very specific fitting instructions and mounting bracket so all of the hard work is done !

Kit FM631DPK Includes:
1x FM30 Micron Filtration Unit
1x FM0 Micron Filter Assy
1x Vehicle Specific Bracket
1x Spare 30 Micron Filter
1x Fuel Line Rubber 12mm DFL12
2x Hose Clamps 12mm FMC12
2x Push-on Straight 12mm
2x 1/4” NPT Straight 12mm
2x 1/4” NPT Plug DP733-04
1x 2x Bolts, 2x Nuts, 4x Washers
1x Thread Paste Sealant (6ml Tube)

Download PDF Info >

Install all fittings and plugs with the thread paste.
